Bowleven Plans to Raise $120 Million in Share Placing

-- B y   A m a n d a   J o r d a n
-- 
2011-10-19T06:06:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-19/bowleven-plans-to-raise-120-million-in-share-placing.html
Bowleven Plc (BLVN) , a U.K.-listed oil
explorer focused on  Africa , said it plans to raise about $120
million in a placing of new shares with new and existing
institutional investors.  To contact the reporter on this story:
